{"tid":2151014,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"襲警被捕後全身傷兼眼角膜受損 官裁定受警威嚇剔除招認口供 今午裁決","createTime":"2020-08-11T07:39:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-11T09:04:56.000Z","uid":56115,"like":48,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"0f70c3e580bb11c0b60cc7a3b78c078db3ad2de7","tid":2151014,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T07:39:44.000Z","msg":"去年10.1有市民將立法會議員何君堯的相片貼在港鐵太子站外，便衣警見狀將文宣「踢甩」，引發警民衝突。中年漢被指踢了警員一腳，遭多名防暴警圍毆，繼而被控襲警罪，案件今在西九龍裁判法院續審。裁判官林子勤指，<span class=\"red\">被告事後傷勢嚴重、眼角膜受損，但警方卻將他扣押30小時</span>、完成三份會面紀錄後才將被告送院。林官認為，被告當時不適合在未經診治下錄取口供，並指招認是在警員威逼和誘導下作出，裁定警方錄取的三份警誡會面紀錄全不可呈堂。被告面對的襲警罪表證成立，將於今午裁決。<br />\n<br />\n辯方又指，警員多次以粗口辱罵被告兼毆打被告，被告更聽到警員<span class=\"red\">揚言「打人唔使講良心」</span><br />\n<br />\n被告被控去年10月1日於港鐵太子站 B1 出口襲擊警員梁偉嘉。<br />\n<br />\n【案件編號：WKCC3815/19】"},{"pid":"a6d465c74af3c850a403e992b6799f139a72422b","tid":2151014,"uid":56115,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T07:39:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200811/6OZKYPZUTQMBOCBXI7ZLMELUOE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200811%2F6OZKYPZUTQMBOCBXI7ZLMELUOE%2F&d=9ox5Qr7lvCKhSYdyRcf9FhmJq4DTS581XL85RX03pBc%3D&h=8d49b0bf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200811%2F6OZKYPZUTQMBOCBXI7ZLMELUOE%2F&h=a68bd991\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200811/6OZKYPZUTQMBOCBXI7ZLMELUOE/</a>"},{"pid":"92d104b13541c09e59481a6a6ffa5da350f1df6b","tid":2151014,"uid":11291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T07:41:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0e725262a0c5956b711446182b46b8612694f49","tid":2151014,"uid":53379,"like":3,"dislike":0,"scor